Available Tools: get_stock_level | check_availability | get_low_stock_items | get_stock_by_location
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "sku": "string", "location_id": "string", "threshold": number }
Response Schema: { "sku": "string", "product_name": "string", "quantity": number, "location": "string", "status": "in_stock|low_stock|out_of_stock" }
---
Question: Determine if we have sufficient Bluetooth speakers in the Boston warehouse, given a reorder point of 40 units.
Call: { "func_call": "check_availability", "sku": "SPK-BT-RED", "location_id": "BOS-WH-13", "threshold": 40 }
Response: { "sku": "SPK-BT-RED", "product_name": "Bluetooth Speaker Red", "quantity": 18, "location": "BOS-WH-13", "status": "low_stock" }

Question: What is the current inventory count for standing desks at our Phoenix distribution center?
Call: { "func_call": "get_stock_level", "sku": "DSK-STD-WHT", "location_id": "PHX-DC-14", "threshold": 0 }
Response: { "sku": "DSK-STD-WHT", "product_name": "Standing Desk White", "quantity": 55, "location": "PHX-DC-14", "status": "in_stock" }

